page.title: 11Family Life
page.content: My name is Jasmin.I am nine years old and have six pets,three fish,two tortoises and a cat.I used to have two cats but one died.I have a brother who is eleven years old. {My name is Nyam Hoa Vuong.I was born in North Vietnam.Neither my father or my mother work;my best friends are Minh and Keith.At home I have got a pool table and I play a lot.I like maths best in school. Hello!My name is Michelle.I am ten years old and have two brothers and one sister.My mam is working but my dad hasn't worked for three years.We have two dogs and one cat named Tiddles.The dogs wake us in the morning because their tails bang on the carpet.
